<section class="about-us-container">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="about-us">About Us</h2>
    <div class="horizontal-line"></div>
    <div class="about-us; margin-top:5px">
      <h2 style="color:black; font-size:18px;text-align:justify"><strong>ToGather</strong> was born out of the shared passion of four individuals from Le Wagon, a leading coding bootcamp, who were driven by the desire to build a stronger sense of community in Singapore. The team recognized the need for a platform that could bring neighbours together, foster social connections and revive the kampung spirit that has been lost in modern society. Drawing on their diverse backgrounds and experiences, they created an avenue to enable people to host activities and share their skills, providing an opportunity for socializing and making new friends while earning money. By doing so, the team aims to create a win-win situation, with economic and social benefits for the community while boosting creativity and providing opportunities for freelancers, stay-home moms, and the elderly to work and share their knowledge about their neighbourhood. With ToGather, the team is proud to contribute to building a more inclusive, connected, and vibrant community in Singapore, and they look forward to seeing the platform grow and make a real difference in people's lives.</h2>
    </div>
