    <div class="horizontal-line"></div>
    <div class="about-us">
      <h2 style="color:black; font-size:18px;text-align:justify">In the past, Singapore's kampung spirit was alive and vibrant, with neighbors coming together to form close-knit communities. However, modernization and our increasingly hectic lifestyles have led to a decline in these connections. At <strong>Togather</strong>, we believe that it's important to bring people back together and foster a sense of community spirit.
      That's why our platform is a combination of <strong><i>"together"</i></strong> and <strong><i>"gather"</i></strong>, two words that embody our mission of bringing people together to form meaningful connections.</h2>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
